  "description": "Organon's variational free-energy metabolism controls how much signal enters Overdub's dub loop — the organism's biochemical state is the send knob. High metabolic activity floods the delay; low activity starves it to a whisper. ModToMod coupling: organon_metabolicRate → dub_sendAmount, amount 0.72. The enzyme becomes the engineer. Biology replaces automation.",
